com.esri.mo2.src.sys
Interface WritableContent

All Superinterfaces:
Comparable, Content, Serializable
All Known Subinterfaces:
WritableFolder
public interface WritableContent
extends Content

Folders may optionally produce Content that is writable depending on the access rights of the user. The Content implementation that is writable must implement WritableContent.
